name: Through The Force Things You Will See
Lore: 'One training exercise for a Jedi''s apprentice is to invert one''s view to see things from a different perspective. ''The future, the past. Old friends long gone.''',
Text: 'At the end of any player''s draw phase, cause that player to place Used Pile face up on top of Reserve Deck. Shuffle, cut, and replace. When face up cards are removed from Reserve Deck, they are treated as normal (no longer face up).',
